        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Moses Austin on John Butler.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><persName>Mr. John Butler</persName></p>

<p>Sr; pay sixty days after date unto <persName>Mr A Gallatan </persName>or Order two
Hundred and Seventy Dollars, it being for value recvd of him this
<date when="1810-03-02">2 day of March 1810</date></p>

<p><persName>Moses Austin</persName></p>
<p><placeName>Saint Louis</placeName> $270$</p>

<p>[Endorsements:] <persName>Mr Butler</persName> please to pay the within to The <persName>Barer</persName>
<persName>Isaac L Morton</persName> and oblige</p>

<p><persName>Abm Gallatin</persName></p>

<p><placeName>Hereulaneum </placeName><date when="1810-03-13">March 13. 1810</date> I will pay the with in order in the
time mentioned.</p>

<p><persName>John Butler</persName></p>

<p>Rec'd <placeName>St Louis</placeName> <date when="1810-10-30">30th Octr 1810</date> of <persName>M. Austin</persName>, One hundred Dollars
on the within&#8212;$100
Red on the within Forty Doll and Forty cents</p>

<p><persName>Jno. Smith</persName></p>
<p><placeName>Hereulaneum </placeName><date when="1810-04-22">April 22nd</date></p>
<p>I will pay the within Balance on demand in Lead at five dollars and
fifty or Cash at Cash price</p>

<p><persName>M Austin</persName></p>

        </div1>
    </body>
